\" class=\"opt\"  > $\\text{A.}$  \u5f53 $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f(x)$ \u5b58\u5728\u65f6, $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f^{\\prime}(x)$ \u5b58\u5728 </span>\r\n                  <span id=\"preview_option2\" class=\"opt\"  > $\\text{B.}$  \u5f53 $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f^{\\prime}(x)$ \u5b58\u5728\u65f6, $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f(x)$ \u5b58\u5728 </span>\r\n                  <span id=\"preview_option3\" class=\"opt\"  > $\\text{C.}$  \u5f53 $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} \\frac{\\int_0^x f(t) d t}{x}$ \u5b58\u5728\u65f6, $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f(x)$ \u5b58\u5728.  </span>\r\n                  <span id=\"preview_option4\" class=\"opt\"   > $\\text{D.}$  \u5f53 $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} f(x)$ \u5b58\u5728\u65f6, $\\lim _{x \\rightarrow+\\infty} \\frac{\\int_0^x f(t) d t}{x}$ \u5b58\u5728.  </span> \r\n              \r\n                    <span id=\"preview_option5\" class=\"opt\"   >   </span> \r\n                  <span id=\"preview_option6\" class=\"opt\"   >   </span> \r\n\r\n                   </div>\r\n\r\n           \r\n \r\n \r\n            \r\n         <div class=\"answer\" style=\"display:none\" ></div>\r\n  \r\n          <br />\r\n\r\n\r\n                <div style=\"clear:both\">\r\n\r\n                </div> \r\n\r\n         </div>\r\n          \r\n\r\n                    \r\n<div class=\"layui-card-foot\"> \r\n  \r\n \r\n\r\n     <span class=\"prop\">\r\n\r\n    <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"detail.aspx?id=21738\">\u67e5\u770b</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"share.aspx?id=21738\">\u5206\u4eab</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n\r\n     <a class=\"vip\" href='ques_new.aspx?id=21738'  target=_blank>\u7f16\u8f91</a> &nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n </span>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"float:right\">  \r\n\r\n     \r\n     <a  class=\"layui-btn layui-btn-warm layui-btn-xs  \"  href=\"###\" onclick=\"Pop('Down_Ti.aspx?id=21738')\" >\u4e0b\u8f7d\u6b64\u9898</a>\r\n        <a  class=\"layui-btn layui-btn-primary layui-btn-